// Embeds app_icon.ico into the DFFastLLM.exe binary itself. Because the
// icon lives inside the executable's resources, Windows automatically uses
// it everywhere: taskbar, Alt+Tab, the .exe file icon in Explorer, and any
// shortcut (desktop, Start Menu) created by the installer that points to
// this .exe — no separate icon file needs to be shipped or referenced.
IDI_APP_ICON ICON "app_icon.ico"
